Communicated by:
ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>

[In addition to the Algerian outbreak last March 2012 referred to below, we have also reported on a serious outbreak in Tunisia above, which was published in this week's OIE WAHID Weekly Disease Information report. While the outbreak in Egypt is not quite as extensive as the one in Tunisia, it still causes concern, especially since this a serious disease in a regionally important species of livestock. - Mod.PC

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: http://healthmap.org/r/1zkM.
